                    android:text="@string/bullets"
                    android:textSize="20sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/TextView06"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_weight="1"
                    android:textSize="20sp"
                    android:textColor="@color/Black"
                    android:text="PVC polymer molecules have positive and negative polarities inside, while plasticiser molecules also have such polar and non-polar parts. The PVC polymer molecules and the plasticizer molecules are electrically attracted to each other, and the non-polar parts widen the distance among the polymer molecules to keep softness. PVC products which are softened by plasticisers are called soft (flexible) PVC products. "/>
            </TableRow>
